  "title": "Certainty of meeting fertility intentions declines in Europe during the 'Great Recession'",
  "abstract": "Relatively little research has been conducted on how economic recessions impact fertility intentions. In particular, uncertainty in reproductive intentions has not been examined in relation to economic shocks.",
